{"tid":2507800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣西男子闖幼稚園斬人 多名幼童浴血躺地","createTime":"2021-04-28T09:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T10:23:28.000Z","uid":391580,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c675970579d98b46fb98278ebcdd4dc69388aa23","tid":2507800,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平正在廣西考察，當地隨即傳出嚴重傷人案；一名25歲男子於周三（28日）下午約2時突然闖入廣西北流市新豐鎮健樂幼兒園，並持刀襲擊老師和學生，導致多人受傷，多名幼童浴血躺在地上。該男子現時已被警方拘捕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcPxouAgVbd25J6oZaTBRb3L5VwBiAFZnWZrQUNjiAZRm?filename=tbhEM2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbhEM2u.jpg&h=cea0b378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRY5iwtqndfRAb35fhD32y8rLYcgkpSqU1xv1iqQz7vgE?filename=QuDAknB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuDAknB.jpg&h=badc7b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPeAhjQ6pkPTz4ui8ckRsNGwAP4mkJtytQkCdJEAkMrn8?filename=M0E0wun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0E0wun.jpg&h=4feeff53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSCZtAiFVQ8Nhk3h959n1rUqWthRed7U4HuHirAoFQygT?filename=MvrKdHR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvrKdHR.jpg&h=2eb1e045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWbhSTASkJydB8kKBSah8TZgsF8MvS64h7RsG6c7XQXyp?filename=mZLZM2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZLZM2Y.jpg&h=d3dee985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYffuZ7zD6hJZVFXVmJvCiR2qZLCeDtyGhnMeRXh2K5g4?filename=ELBBPgp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELBBPgp.jpg&h=c8a977e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內媒引述現場一名目擊者指，當日他路過北流市新豐鎮健樂幼兒園時，看到一名男子正被3名警員從幼兒園內押送出來，「還有小孩子頭部流着血從幼兒園裏出來。」附近一名商舖老闆亦表示，男疑犯年紀不大，其行為舉止似乎有些異常；後來有路人看到該男子持刀斬人後，便拿着木棍衝進幼兒園內將其圍住，警方隨後到場將其制伏。<br />\n<br />\n傷者現時正在新豐鎮衛生院接受治療。警方表示，男疑犯的年齡約25歲，現時已被拘捕，並強調他「可能精神有問題」；至於事件中有多名老師和學生受傷，部分受傷較嚴重的正在接受搶救。"},{"pid":"46515372b109ab1d7f4cc6c7528bed1d42757947","tid":2507800,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ridBF-RldSWgUzJsrs2FSNKwRC8=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NRC7BNTYTV5ULT725YCQ5T4AVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FridBF-RldSWgUzJsrs2FSNKwRC8%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNRC7BNTYTV5ULT725YCQ5T4AVM.jpg&h=d473d43c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f9a9cd51d6b5a93f7e1bd09a55da5bf7c8cf361","tid":2507800,"uid":55458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"湖人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n占士班太監fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecac64d6053b3d6d62978c25e55458cc7961337b","tid":2507800,"uid":196949,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"又係個淨係識得斬細佬嘅懦夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f584d59b5f3fa96f9ac000101c7554d9c69826da","tid":2507800,"uid":182624,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"有貪官唔斬去斬小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5299b7a7d3e1f26f997615b9be1044c9f81f020a","tid":2507800,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f584d59b